high_descs: Walk forward to the wall, then go right and walk to the table.
Pick up the tomato.
Turn right and walk around the counter to get to the stove and microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn right, head towards the corner of the room on the left past the end of the counter. Face the trash can.
Throw the tomato in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right and walk for a step before turning left and walking to the wall turning right when you hit it to stand by the circular white table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Go to the other side of the room and stand by the stove so you are facing it.
Cook the tomato in the microwave and then take it back out closing the microwave when you have retrieved the tomato.
Walk back to the other side of the room and stand in front of the garbage.
Put the tomato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato in the garbage.

high_descs: Move to the large round white table where the tomato is sitting
Pick up the tomato on top of the white table
Carry the tomato to the microwave above the stove top
Place the tomato in the microwave, heat it then remove it
Carry the tomato to the trash can at the end of the counter top on the floor
Place the tomato in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Carry a heated tomato to the trash

high_descs: Walk ahead and hang right to the table on the right.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn right and walk around the counter and ahead to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around and veer left to the end of the counter.
Put the tomato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a trash bin.

high_descs: move to the table to the right of the sink
pick up a tomato from the table
move to the microwave to the left of the fridge
heat the tomato in the microwave
move to the bin at the end of the counter to the left
put the tomato in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the bin.

high_descs: Walk across the kitchen to the round white table
Pick up the tomato from the table
Turn around and walk through the kitchen to the microwave
Put the tomato into the microwave and cook it
Take the tomato and walk over to the trash can at the end of the counter
Put the tomato into the trash can
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato into the trash can
